But do you know that Vaseline is not good for the skin? I have read that it is basically a byproduct that gets produced in the oil industry, the same place where they produce gas and diesel. Also, it's inaccurate to say that Vaseline gives moisture - all it does is just keep the moisture in your lips/skin from escaping. So it can have the benefit of locking in moisture, but still, applying onto skin will clog your pores and prevent the toxins from getting out!
